{"tid":731522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這群「台妹」，為什麼選擇到 大陸 升學?","createTime":"2018-07-06T08:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T08:15:19.000Z","uid":53060,"like":5,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2b31af4c7286b2694ffe2c89c954a5f98b25b3","tid":731522,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:50:13.000Z","msg":"18歲的夏天，這些高中生決定離開台灣，到中國大陸讀大學。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>是在台灣考不上好大學？台灣的大學競爭力不足？看好中國的大學比較有國際觀？還是趁大學提早在中國大陸市場卡位？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本文由端傳媒和台灣公共電視《獨立特派員》共同編輯、發佈。公共電視為非營利機構，本文免費開放閱讀。電視報導於七月四日晚間十點於台灣公共電頻道首播，也將於《獨立特派員》網站完整發表。<br />\n<br />\n原文：《台灣這群準大學生，為什麼選擇西進？》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20180704-taiwan-pts-taiwanese-chinauniversity/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20180704-taiwan-pts-taiwanese-chinauniversity%2F&d=tIRv%2FMGLmht8M4%2Fqae7Cx4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9d6318e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20180704-taiwan-pts-taiwanese-chinauniversity/</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20180704-taiwan-pts-taiwanese-chinauniversity/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20180704-taiwan-pts-taiwanese-chinauniversity%2F&d=tIRv%2FMGLmht8M4%2Fqae7Cx4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9d6318e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20180704-taiwan-pts-taiwanese-chinauniversity/</a>"},{"pid":"31d88496650b8215be9346011cb7ec76c2ba9b01","tid":731522,"uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":60,"score":-59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"江宇晴在台灣被交通大學材料科學系取錄，在中國則面試廈門大學、浙江大學及南京大學，最後三所都錄取，兩岸四個校系放在一起比較，浙江大學計算機科學系最符合自己的志向。攝影：賴振元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2018/07/87d0d4843e194f9596ce60c44f9cb94a.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2F87d0d4843e194f9596ce60c44f9cb94a.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=482804cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江宇晴說，自己是把大陸和台灣「穿插在一起的」，所以對她而言，是依學校來選擇不是依地區。 為什麼選擇中國大陸的大學？江宇晴說，<span style=\"color: red;\">她一開始的目標其實是香港。香港的大學可以直接用學測成績申請，但自己學測考出來的成績不是很理想，拿不到獎學金，但香港學費又很貴。</span>「我同學是一直在注意大陸那邊的訊息，他就說大陸也有學校，我就想說不試白不試，去投投看好了。」"},{"pid":"4829b14f261ac4a0fe1732e23990934e558b40f3","tid":731522,"uid":83609,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"31d88496650b8215be9346011cb7ec76c2ba9b01","tid":731522,"uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":60,"score":-59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"江宇晴在台灣被交通大學材料科學系取錄，在中國則面試廈門大學、浙江大學及南京大學，最後三所都錄取，兩岸四個校系放在一起比較，浙江大學計算機科學系最符合自己的志向。攝影：賴振元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2018/07/87d0d4843e194f9596ce60c44f9cb94a.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2F87d0d4843e194f9596ce60c44f9cb94a.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=482804cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江宇晴說，自己是把大陸和台灣「穿插在一起的」，所以對她而言，是依學校來選擇不是依地區。 為什麼選擇中國大陸的大學？江宇晴說，<span style=\"color: red;\">她一開始的目標其實是香港。香港的大學可以直接用學測成績申請，但自己學測考出來的成績不是很理想，拿不到獎學金，但香港學費又很貴。</span>「我同學是一直在注意大陸那邊的訊息，他就說大陸也有學校，我就想說不試白不試，去投投看好了。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"唔好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa7430bdad8b120265fe090d40e7b8356a8daed","tid":731522,"uid":53060,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"李昀在台灣已經錄取成功大學，感覺中國尤其在頂尖大學裡，學習的氛圍、學生上進心都跟台灣很不同，受父母鼓勵出來看看，同時申請了浙江大學及廈門大學。攝影：賴振元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2018/07/c602360fb41741ef942785b1107fac62.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2Fc602360fb41741ef942785b1107fac62.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=ac03d1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李昀在台灣已經被成功大學錄取，在中國大陸同時申請浙江大學及廈門大學。她說，透過媒體的報導，感覺中國變得很不一樣，尤其在頂尖大學裡，學習的氛圍、學生上進心都跟台灣很不同，加上父母以前也是台商，很鼓勵自己出來看看。但她也擔心班上有學霸同學，已經先請舅舅寄大陸高考的書去台灣，趁暑假就要開始研讀，先一步了解同學們的實力。<br />\n<br />\n除了公立高中，台灣私立明星高中流行畢業出國讀書，中國也已經成重要選項。台北私立復興高中的張瀚文、陳昀萱及彭琳，在台灣分別已經申請上政治大學、中央大學及清華大學，但三人還是結伴一起到廈門大學面試。三人接著還要一起搭動車往廣州，參加中山大學的面試。陳昀萱說，復興高中原本每年就都有三分之一的畢業生，會選擇出國念大學，過去大多是申請英美學校，這兩年到中國的人數也逐漸在攀升。"},{"pid":"891df30fa0f816f14ecc4017bb0183aa9447cdca","tid":731522,"uid":20241,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"樣衰下話"},{"pid":"1fa76d93798b2656a449c29b5d0674362f3d8037","tid":731522,"uid":48083,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"e2e1eaa254520e68cb8512a4b70faf66591c64c7","tid":731522,"uid":157193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31d88496650b8215be9346011cb7ec76c2ba9b01","tid":731522,"uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":60,"score":-59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"江宇晴在台灣被交通大學材料科學系取錄，在中國則面試廈門大學、浙江大學及南京大學，最後三所都錄取，兩岸四個校系放在一起比較，浙江大學計算機科學系最符合自己的志向。攝影：賴振元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2018/07/87d0d4843e194f9596ce60c44f9cb94a.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2F87d0d4843e194f9596ce60c44f9cb94a.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=482804cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江宇晴說，自己是把大陸和台灣「穿插在一起的」，所以對她而言，是依學校來選擇不是依地區。 為什麼選擇中國大陸的大學？江宇晴說，<span style=\"color: red;\">她一開始的目標其實是香港。香港的大學可以直接用學測成績申請，但自己學測考出來的成績不是很理想，拿不到獎學金，但香港學費又很貴。</span>「我同學是一直在注意大陸那邊的訊息，他就說大陸也有學校，我就想說不試白不試，去投投看好了。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"點睇都唔似「妹」喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af952cccf575921f4a0e20e1b2c521aa37421472","tid":731522,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n唔知有幾啱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/191407_491efdb8e8c580e887c73ba96c6caa66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F191407_491efdb8e8c580e887c73ba96c6caa66.png&h=8a3fb2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/191410_9223eb7c758625a0eca876b749e2bcc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F191410_9223eb7c758625a0eca876b749e2bcc0.png&h=3f40358f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/191414_c43b1b46bede0e0634fe759b842774d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F191414_c43b1b46bede0e0634fe759b842774d8.png&h=a147a68a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/191420_a892386ab3648403d928934bd3b9527a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F191420_a892386ab3648403d928934bd3b9527a.png&h=091b075a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/caojitw/status/1011807836442017793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fcaojitw%2Fstatus%2F1011807836442017793&d=tIRv%2FMGLmht8M4%2Fqae7Cx4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cb13d562\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/caojitw/status/1011807836442017793</a>"},{"pid":"4ff974c96d55786035b57baada38315c378e601f","tid":731522,"uid":8410,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"呢班係台妹？同平時見開嗰d差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4614c9bc03bdd5e3f7395a3bc503a61fdb967ee","tid":731522,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"樣衰去到邊都比人杯架啦"},{"pid":"9d002b924b9cd6b55390363f0698c9f0e5521d28","tid":731522,"uid":53060,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:55:52.000Z","msg":"「如果人才就這樣全部都被一網打盡了，台灣還剩什麼？」<br />\n<br />\n每年申請放榜後，師大附中穿堂總會貼出榜單，今年多了許多中國大陸跟香港的學校，李志麟也在其中，他錄取了北京大學醫學系。「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>北京大學的學費應該很便宜，而且他會給我很多補助，我等於說我在那邊念的話，我躺著呼吸我就賺錢。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸的學校招生「用力」的程度讓人難以想像。李志麟的父親李明錡就接到北大醫學系的老師直接打電話來。「 對！他就是要你這個人。 這個我以前很難以想像，他就是希望能夠把這個高分群(的學生)，真的都被鎖在大陸念書。」接了電話，李明錡說自己突然感受到，「如果人才就這樣全部都被一網打盡了，台灣還剩什麼？」<br />\n<br />\n但他還是要留在台灣？他點點頭說，因為若是去了中國大陸，就沒有辦法在台灣行醫。感覺在台灣學完，沒有辦法回饋社會的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n想留在台灣，那當初幹嘛去申請？「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為感覺上一個北京大學會感覺：歐，好像很棒。 所以就去申請一下北京大學。</strong></span>」"},{"pid":"8b702c84c4bc164cfb27d4a31d73b91c0b9de777","tid":731522,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"周恩來：中國的妓女在台灣"},{"pid":"bedad674359a3b404c04c5496fd25e3351e714fc","tid":731522,"uid":169310,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"大陸人黎台灣讀書做跳板去美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你就走返去中國做白老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台灣考唔到醫工科真係去大陸算吧啦。其他科都係垃圾"},{"pid":"b265ee8a3a9533319209c306c581b933aaabaafe","tid":731522,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"因為太低質係台灣無啖好食？"},{"pid":"943737bc492913c4f298543d0673124fd95304f8","tid":731522,"uid":60635,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"吹水吹咁大，有成功交通唔讀，去讀19 浙江大學 廈門大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076865ec1923b03fe8dfabef98e1a9a9c7bff8fd","tid":731522,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"樣貌同智力應該係有關係"},{"pid":"cab995528bf5184cf384b4577d1b16ce752d68bd","tid":731522,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"會窮"},{"pid":"39113ae10a3a5d1a0f5c12f3a16979815f1114fe","tid":731522,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"連大陸人都走資嘅今日，都仲衝去大陸<br />\n真係自尋死路"},{"pid":"8eae7a2b788eacc821a8eda1847b4a2b9b68871d","tid":731522,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>江宇晴在台灣被交通大學材料科學系取錄，在中國則面試廈門大學、浙江大學及南京大學，最後三所都錄取，兩岸四個校系放在一起比較，浙江大學計算機科學系最符合自己的志向。攝影：賴振元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2018/07/87d0d4843e194f9596ce60c44f9cb94a.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2F87d0d4843e194f9596ce60c44f9cb94a.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=482804cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江宇晴說，自己是把大陸和台灣「穿插在一起的」，所以對她而言，是依學校來選擇不是依地區。 為什麼選擇中國大陸的大學？江宇晴說，<span style=\"color: red;\">她一開始的目標其實是香港。香港的大學可以直接用學測成績申請，但自己學測考出來的成績不是很理想，拿不到獎學金，但香港學費又很貴。</span>「我同學是一直在注意大陸那邊的訊息，他就說大陸也有學校，我就想說不試白不試，去投投看好了。」</blockquote>唔好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得揀咩 比唔起學費 唔通賣身賺學費之後比你地叫做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475124acc24460d027668f886ed2d1e16534645c","tid":731522,"uid":79410,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"943737bc492913c4f298543d0673124fd95304f8","tid":731522,"uid":60635,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"吹水吹咁大，有成功交通唔讀，去讀19 浙江大學 廈門大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:17:55.000Z","msg":"浙大係勁嘢嚟. <br />\n廈門就算啦<br />\n如果成功同浙大. 一定係讀浙大."},{"pid":"ff21ebf184e0caa7806a35d89e868019e8f0d